mTLS (Mutual TLS) Certificates

X.509 certificate issuance process
Certificate lifecycle: issuance, renewal, revocation
Private key security requirements
Certificate storage in HashiCorp Vault
API Keys & Tokens

Generation and rotation policies
Scope and permissions model
Secure storage and transmission
Emergency revocation procedures
Network Security

IP whitelisting requirements
VPN or dedicated circuit options
Firewall rules and security groups
DDoS protection considerations
